---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'IV Therapy | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Personalized IV drips delivering vitamins, minerals, electrolytes, and fluids for rapid hydration and targeted support—administered by trained professionals.',
  canonical: '/services/iv-therapy/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'IV Therapy',
      serviceType: 'Wellness & IV',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/iv-therapy/',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      }
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Wellness & IV</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">IV Therapy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        Customized intravenous infusions to support hydration and targeted nutrients. Evidence for many wellness
        uses can be limited in healthy individuals—your provider will personalize recommendations.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Delivery</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Intravenous drip</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Session time</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">20–60+ minutes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">None to minimal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Best for</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Hydration & support</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">

      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            IV therapy delivers fluids, vitamins, minerals, and electrolytes directly into the bloodstream, bypassing
            digestion for rapid availability. It is commonly used for hydration support, travel recovery, and targeted
            nutrient delivery. For generally healthy people, evidence for some wellness claims is mixed; our approach
            prioritizes safety, medical review, and realistic expectations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Potential benefits</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              {[
                'Rapid hydration and electrolyte replenishment',
                'Direct delivery for those with absorption challenges',
                'Customizable blends tailored to goals',
                'Low downtime and clinic-based monitoring'
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
              Not a substitute for balanced nutrition or medical care. Your provider will advise whether IV is appropriate.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            We begin with a health review (medical history, medications, allergies) and, when appropriate, labs to
            guide formulation. You’ll receive a tailored blend and monitored infusion in a comfortable setting.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">During your visit</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>IV catheter placed using aseptic technique</li>
                <li>Drip over 20–60+ minutes depending on volume</li>
                <li>Warmth or mild tingling can occur and is usually brief</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Immediate feel</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Most resume normal activity right away</li>
                <li>Many report feeling refreshed and hydrated</li>
                <li>Effects vary with baseline status and formula</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Popular drips (examples) -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Popular drip examples</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          {[
            {
              name: 'Hydration',
              items: ['Electrolytes + fluids', 'Replenishes after travel or exertion', 'Gentle, foundational support']
            },
            {
              name: 'Immune support',
              items: ['Vitamin C + zinc (as appropriate)', 'Antioxidant-focused', 'Used seasonally or during recovery']
            },
            {
              name: 'Beauty/Glow',
              items: ['Hydration + skin-supportive nutrients', 'Pairs with healthy skin habits', 'May be cycled in series']
            }
          ].map(card => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">{card.name}</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                {card.items.map(i => <li>{i}</li>)}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Formulas are customized and may be adjusted based on health status, labs, and tolerance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Stay hydrated orally for the rest of the day.</li>
              <li>Take it easy if you feel lightheaded or fatigued.</li>
              <li>Avoid intense heat (sauna/steam) immediately after.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Monitor the IV site; report persistent redness, warmth, or swelling.</li>
              <li>Avoid duplicating high-dose vitamins without guidance.</li>
              <li>Follow your personalized schedule for future sessions.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & risks</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, mild effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Tenderness or bruise at the IV site</li>
              <li>Temporary warmth or metallic taste (formula dependent)</li>
              <li>Mild fatigue if dehydrated prior to infusion</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Less common, more serious</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Infection or phlebitis at the IV site</li>
              <li>Electrolyte imbalance or fluid overload in at-risk patients</li>
              <li>Allergic reactions or vitamin/mineral toxicity at high doses</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Important precautions</div>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1.5">
            <li>Disclose heart, kidney, or liver conditions before treatment.</li>
            <li>Discuss pregnancy or lactation with your provider.</li>
            <li>Report all medications and supplements.</li>
            <li>Infusions should be clinically justified—avoid frequent drips without monitoring.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How often can I do IV therapy?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Frequency depends on goals, health status, and labs. We avoid indiscriminate, frequent drips without
              medical oversight.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Will I feel instantly revitalized?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Many report feeling refreshed, especially if dehydrated; effects vary and can be modest in those without
              deficiencies.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Is IV better than oral vitamins?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Not universally. IV can help when absorption is compromised or deficiency is documented; otherwise, oral
              options are often sufficient and lower risk.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How much does it cost?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Pricing depends on formula, volume, and clinical time. We’ll provide transparent options during consult.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Ready to personalize an IV plan that fits your goals and health history?
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
